Start running your business better today.

Support for current ADP accounts »    Employees ›    Administrators ›





Get comprehensive HR technology and expertise with ADP.
There’s a lot that goes into managing your employees, from running payroll and tracking time to cultivating talent and administering benefits. We’ll help you keep things streamlined, accessible, and easy to manage –so you can focus on what you do best.



Payroll Services
 


Time and Attendance
 


Human Resource Management
 


Benefits Administration
 


Talent Management
 
 

 



Get payroll services for the way you work.

Payroll isn’t just about a paycheck. Labor is likely your biggest cost, and it touches many parts of your business. Do it right with ADP.
Better payroll services mean:

Lower risk of compliance-related issues and penalties
Vast reductions in administrative time, effort, and money
Anytime, anywhere access for HR managers and employees
Increased efficiency across every areas of your business that intersects with payroll




“Not having to worry about payroll really allows us to focus on our core competencies and servicing our customers.”
Brandon McKennon 
Partner, BreezeIT



 



Boost productivity with time and attendance.




ADP’s automated tracking can save 40 minutes per week per manager.
Source: Nucleus Research, K60 Guidebook ADP, October 2010




Tracking time can be a hassle—but it doesn’t have to be. In fact, smart time and labor management lead to better decision-making for your business overall. 
We’ll help you:

Figure out if you have the right number of employees
Control costs through enhanced time and attendance tracking
Accommodate and multi-language workforce
Understand what Health Care Reform means for time and attendance tracking




 



Make HR a strategic part of your business.

By streamlining administrative HR processes, we’ll help you focus on empowering your people, and aligning individual performance to your business objectives.
You’ll get:

Simple HR processes and workflows
Strategies that you can implement today, and protect you for tomorrow
Ways to connect your workforce to your company goals






69% of businesses that migrated from an in-house solution to an outsourced model reported favorable results.
Source: 2011 BlessingWhite Employee Engagement Report, Hewitt Associates






 



Simplify benefits administration for yourself – and your staff.

Benefits should support your overall talent strategy, and simply must stay up-to-date with changing Affordable Care Act (ACA) regulations. 
We’ll help you:

Attract the best and the bright with world-class retirement and insurance plans
Achieve higher employee satisfaction through better benefits administration worldwide
Access more affordable benefits for your workforce
Provide an open enrollment experience that’s as easy as online shopping
Reduce the time, energy, and headcount associated with benefits administration
Take control of ACA regulations




“ADP has provided a lot of resources to us in understanding the Affordable Care Act. It’s the information we need in one source – it saves us time trying to research all those subjects we need to understand.”
David Laverentz 
VP Finance and Administration, Kansas City Royals



 



Build a company of superstars with talent management.

Good talent management means looking ahead, removing obstacles, and fostering excellence—no matter how big or small your business is.
Imagine being able to:

Recognize a new hire’s potential before they even start
Spot small holes in your organization’s talent before they become big ones
Chart a course for every employee that aligns with your company’s larger vision
Ensure that your best people grow – and stay – with you
Have a plan and a process for managing the entire talent lifecycle, including succession management






Lost productivity of actively disengaged employees costs the U.S. economy $370 billion annually.
Source: 2010 Gallup Employee Engagement Survey






 



